dc_description_s: The PLSS data set shows lines and polygons of the Public Land Survey System, including Townships, Sections, Quarter Sections, and sixteenth section divisions.             The data was developed to the highest accuracy standards to support the construction of Integrated Land Records (ILR) data. Older, less accurate data sets may not register with this data.             The master copy of PLSS data for Snohomish County is maintained by the Assessor's Office. PLSS has been derived from the master copy and reformatted by DIS to facilitate display, query, and analysis.
